readme:
Service Usage

This service will match a party in CDH by the document details with the purpose of finding one single best match for the details currently provided.Multiple results can be returned.

Service Behaviour

Traveller Platform lodges SV341 call to Client Data Hub using Document details to obtain best match results. Filters containing Biographic details and Generic Identifiers can be applied to narrow down results.
